message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY. This paper is about a task related to community question answering, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the use of different approaches and features by participating systems suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the inclusion of an Arabic subtask may indicate the involvement of computational linguistics (cs.CY).
